That's hot!

384
00:28:03,061 --> 00:28:04,228
You bitch!

385
00:28:05,496 --> 00:28:07,332
Are you aware of
the word "manners",

386
00:28:07,357 --> 00:28:09,233
or do you really not have any?

387
00:28:10,485 --> 00:28:13,363
I am perfectly aware of
how I conduct my actions

388
00:28:13,388 --> 00:28:16,557
in accordance with
accepted norms.

389
00:28:16,939 --> 00:28:17,994
What?

390
00:28:18,019 --> 00:28:22,872
Unfortunately, I found that to be
the safest and most suitable way

391
00:28:22,872 --> 00:28:27,543
