you and my husband.

392
00:28:32,025 --> 00:28:33,025
So...

393
00:28:34,299 --> 00:28:35,634
You're Aemie?

394
00:28:37,402 --> 00:28:38,402
Obviously.

395
00:28:39,263 --> 00:28:40,637
Who else would it be?

396
00:28:42,141 --> 00:28:46,229
Well, Aemie,
I'm Fiona Stonehurst.

397
00:28:48,398 --> 00:28:50,775
So glad to finally meet you.

398
00:28:51,150 --> 00:28:55,571
Ezekiel actually mentioned
you while he was in Hawaii.

399
00:28:56,489 --> 00:28:57,615
With me.

400
00:28:58,116 --> 00:28:59,116
Oh!

401
00:28:59,700 --> 00:29:00,700
He did?

402
00:29:01,202 --> 00:29:02,202
Aw,

403
