thanks for accompanying
my husband.

404
00:29:04,956 --> 00:29:06,416
My husband.

405
00:29:08,501 --> 00:29:09,502
You know what, Aemie?

406
00:29:10,294 --> 00:29:14,757
I actually think that you
and I have a lot in common.

407
00:29:15,633 --> 00:29:19,205
I mean, for Ezekiel
to like the both of us,

408
00:29:19,512 --> 00:29:23,391
